cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SI

This paper deals with the design of feedback quantizers for networked control systems, which involves topics related to control systems (cs.SY), information theory (cs.IT), and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of Delta-Sigma modulators also suggests a possible connection to neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper discusses the impact of quantization on the system performance, which is a topic related to signal processing (cs.SI).
